      • DoubleFeature

        public DoubleFeature(double startTimeMsec,
                     double endTimeMsec,
                     Vector x,
                     double[] y)
        Create the feature with the given independent and dependent arrays of values.
        Parameters:
        x - an array of values sorted in order. If not in ascending order, then the instance will store a new array that is sorted as such.
        y - actual features corresponding to the values in x. If x is resorted, then y is also resorted.
